{
  "video_id": "folTvNDL08A",
  "title": "David Deutsch: A new way to explain explanation",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 23330.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure that, throughout the hundred-thousand-odd years"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 23330.0,
      "end_time": 26330.0,
      "text": "of our species&#39; existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 26330.0,
      "end_time": 29330.0,
      "text": "and even before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 29330.0,
      "end_time": 31330.0,
      "text": "our ancestors looked up at the night sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31330.0,
      "end_time": 34330.0,
      "text": "and wondered what stars are."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34330.0,
      "end_time": 36330.0,
      "text": "Wondering, therefore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36330.0,
      "end_time": 40330.0,
      "text": "how to explain what they saw"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40330.0,
      "end_time": 45330.0,
      "text": "in terms of things unseen."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45330.0,
      "end_time": 49330.0,
      "text": "Okay, so, most people"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 49330.0,
      "end_time": 52330.0,
      "text": "only wondered that occasionally, like today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52330.0,
      "end_time": 54330.0,
      "text": "in breaks from whatever"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54330.0,
      "end_time": 56330.0,
      "text": "normally preoccupied them."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56330.0,
      "end_time": 60330.0,
      "text": "But what normally preoccupied them"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60330.0,
      "end_time": 63330.0,
      "text": "also involved yearning to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63330.0,
      "end_time": 66330.0,
      "text": "They wished they knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66330.0,
      "end_time": 68330.0,
      "text": "how to prevent their food supply"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68330.0,
      "end_time": 70330.0,
      "text": "from sometimes failing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70330.0,
      "end_time": 73330.0,
      "text": "and how they could rest when they were tired"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73330.0,
      "end_time": 77330.0,
      "text": "without risking starvation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77330.0,
      "end_time": 81330.0,
      "text": "be warmer, cooler, safer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81330.0,
      "end_time": 83330.0,
      "text": "in less pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83330.0,
      "end_time": 86330.0,
      "text": "I bet those prehistoric cave artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86330.0,
      "end_time": 88330.0,
      "text": "would have loved to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88330.0,
      "end_time": 90330.0,
      "text": "how to draw better."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90330.0,
      "end_time": 95330.0,
      "text": "In every aspect of their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 95330.0,
      "end_time": 100330.0,
      "text": "they wished for progress, just as we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100330.0,
      "end_time": 106330.0,
      "text": "But they failed, almost completely, to make any."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106330.0,
      "end_time": 109330.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t know how to."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 109330.0,
      "end_time": 113330.0,
      "text": "Discoveries like fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113330.0,
      "end_time": 117330.0,
      "text": "happened so rarely, that from an individual&#39;s point of view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117330.0,
      "end_time": 120330.0,
      "text": "the world never improved."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120330.0,
      "end_time": 124330.0,
      "text": "Nothing new was learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 124330.0,
      "end_time": 127330.0,
      "text": "The first clue to the origin of starlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 127330.0,
      "end_time": 134329.0,
      "text": "happened as recently as 1899: radioactivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134330.0,
      "end_time": 136330.0,
      "text": "Within 40 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136330.0,
      "end_time": 140330.0,
      "text": "physicists discovered the whole explanation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 140330.0,
      "end_time": 145330.0,
      "text": "expressed, as usual, in elegant symbols."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 145330.0,
      "end_time": 147330.0,
      "text": "But never mind the symbols."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 147330.0,
      "end_time": 151330.0,
      "text": "Think how many discoveries"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 151330.0,
      "end_time": 153330.0,
      "text": "they represent."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 153330.0,
      "end_time": 156330.0,
      "text": "Nuclei and nuclear reactions, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156330.0,
      "end_time": 163330.0,
      "text": "But isotopes, particles of electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 163330.0,
      "end_time": 167330.0,
      "text": "antimatter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 167330.0,
      "end_time": 169330.0,
      "text": "neutrinos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 169330.0,
      "end_time": 173330.0,
      "text": "the conversion of mass to energy -- that&#39;s E=mc^2 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 173330.0,
      "end_time": 175330.0,
      "text": "gamma rays,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 175330.0,
      "end_time": 179330.0,
      "text": "transmutation."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 179330.0,
      "end_time": 184330.0,
      "text": "That ancient dream that had always eluded the alchemists"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 184330.0,
      "end_time": 186330.0,
      "text": "was achieved through these same theories"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 186330.0,
      "end_time": 188330.0,
      "text": "that explained starlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 188330.0,
      "end_time": 191330.0,
      "text": "and other ancient mysteries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 191330.0,
      "end_time": 194330.0,
      "text": "and new, unexpected phenomena."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 194330.0,
      "end_time": 198330.0,
      "text": "That all that, discovered in 40 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 198330.0,
      "end_time": 201330.0,
      "text": "had not been in the previous hundred thousand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 201330.0,
      "end_time": 205330.0,
      "text": "was not for lack of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 205330.0,
      "end_time": 209330.0,
      "text": "about stars, and all those other urgent problems they had."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 209330.0,
      "end_time": 212330.0,
      "text": "They even arrived at answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 212330.0,
      "end_time": 214330.0,
      "text": "such as myths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 214330.0,
      "end_time": 216330.0,
      "text": "that dominated their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 216330.0,
      "end_time": 220330.0,
      "text": "yet bore almost no resemblance"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 220330.0,
      "end_time": 222330.0,
      "text": "to the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 222330.0,
      "end_time": 227330.0,
      "text": "The tragedy of that protracted stagnation"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 227330.0,
      "end_time": 229330.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t sufficiently recognized, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 229330.0,
      "end_time": 231330.0,
      "text": "These were people with brains of"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 231330.0,
      "end_time": 234330.0,
      "text": "essentially the same design"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234330.0,
      "end_time": 239330.0,
      "text": "that eventually did discover all those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 239330.0,
      "end_time": 243330.0,
      "text": "But that ability to make progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 243330.0,
      "end_time": 246330.0,
      "text": "remained almost unused,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 246330.0,
      "end_time": 249330.0,
      "text": "until the event that"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 249330.0,
      "end_time": 251330.0,
      "text": "revolutionized the human condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251330.0,
      "end_time": 253330.0,
      "text": "and changed the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 253330.0,
      "end_time": 255330.0,
      "text": "Or so we should hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 255330.0,
      "end_time": 257330.0,
      "text": "Because that event was the"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 257329.0,
      "end_time": 259329.0,
      "text": "Scientific Revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259329.0,
      "end_time": 261329.0,
      "text": "ever since which our knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 261329.0,
      "end_time": 263330.0,
      "text": "of the physical world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 263330.0,
      "end_time": 267330.0,
      "text": "and of how to adapt it to our wishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267330.0,
      "end_time": 269330.0,
      "text": "has been growing relentlessly."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 269330.0,
      "end_time": 272330.0,
      "text": "Now, what had changed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 272330.0,
      "end_time": 274330.0,
      "text": "What were people now doing for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 274330.0,
      "end_time": 276330.0,
      "text": "that made that difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 276330.0,
      "end_time": 278330.0,
      "text": "between stagnation"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 278330.0,
      "end_time": 282330.0,
      "text": "and rapid, open-ended discovery?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282330.0,
      "end_time": 284330.0,
      "text": "How to make that difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284330.0,
      "end_time": 288330.0,
      "text": "is surely the most important universal truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 288330.0,
      "end_time": 290330.0,
      "text": "that it is possible to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 290330.0,
      "end_time": 295330.0,
      "text": "Worryingly, there is no consensus about what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295330.0,
      "end_time": 297330.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;ll tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297330.0,
      "end_time": 301330.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;ll have to backtrack a little first."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 301330.0,
      "end_time": 304330.0,
      "text": "Before the Scientific Revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 304330.0,
      "end_time": 307330.0,
      "text": "they believed that everything important, knowable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 307330.0,
      "end_time": 309330.0,
      "text": "was already known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 309330.0,
      "end_time": 312330.0,
      "text": "enshrined in ancient writings, institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 312330.0,
      "end_time": 315330.0,
      "text": "and in some genuinely useful rules of thumb --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 315330.0,
      "end_time": 319330.0,
      "text": "which were, however, entrenched as dogmas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 319330.0,
      "end_time": 321330.0,
      "text": "along with many falsehoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 321330.0,
      "end_time": 325330.0,
      "text": "So they believed that knowledge came from authorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 325330.0,
      "end_time": 328330.0,
      "text": "that actually knew very little."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 328330.0,
      "end_time": 331330.0,
      "text": "And therefore progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 331330.0,
      "end_time": 334330.0,
      "text": "depended on learning how to reject"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 334330.0,
      "end_time": 337330.0,
      "text": "the authority of learned men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 337330.0,
      "end_time": 341330.0,
      "text": "priests, traditions and rulers."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 341330.0,
      "end_time": 344330.0,
      "text": "Which is why the Scientific Revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 344330.0,
      "end_time": 346330.0,
      "text": "had to have a wider context."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 346330.0,
      "end_time": 350330.0,
      "text": "The Enlightenment, a revolution in how"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 350330.0,
      "end_time": 353330.0,
      "text": "people sought knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 353330.0,
      "end_time": 356330.0,
      "text": "trying not to rely on authority."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 356330.0,
      "end_time": 358330.0,
      "text": "\"Take no one&#39;s word for it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 358330.0,
      "end_time": 362330.0,
      "text": "But that can&#39;t be what made the difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 362330.0,
      "end_time": 364330.0,
      "text": "Authorities had been rejected before, many times."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364330.0,
      "end_time": 366330.0,
      "text": "And that rarely, if ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 366330.0,
      "end_time": 370330.0,
      "text": "caused anything like the Scientific Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 370330.0,
      "end_time": 372330.0,
      "text": "At the time, what they thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 372330.0,
      "end_time": 374330.0,
      "text": "distinguished science"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 374330.0,
      "end_time": 378330.0,
      "text": "was a radical idea about things unseen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 378330.0,
      "end_time": 381330.0,
      "text": "known as empiricism."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 381330.0,
      "end_time": 386330.0,
      "text": "All knowledge derives from the senses."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 386330.0,
      "end_time": 389330.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;ve seen that that can&#39;t be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 389330.0,
      "end_time": 393330.0,
      "text": "It did help by promoting"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 393330.0,
      "end_time": 395330.0,
      "text": "observation and experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 395330.0,
      "end_time": 397330.0,
      "text": "But, from the outset, it was obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 397330.0,
      "end_time": 400330.0,
      "text": "that there was something horribly wrong with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 400330.0,
      "end_time": 402330.0,
      "text": "Knowledge comes from the senses."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 402330.0,
      "end_time": 405330.0,
      "text": "In what language? Certainly not the language of mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 405330.0,
      "end_time": 408330.0,
      "text": "in which, Galileo rightly said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 408330.0,
      "end_time": 411330.0,
      "text": "the book of nature is written."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 411330.0,
      "end_time": 414330.0,
      "text": "Look at the world. You don&#39;t see equations"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 414330.0,
      "end_time": 417330.0,
      "text": "carved on to the mountainsides."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 417330.0,
      "end_time": 419330.0,
      "text": "If you did, it would be because people"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 419330.0,
      "end_time": 421330.0,
      "text": "had carved them."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 421330.0,
      "end_time": 424330.0,
      "text": "By the way, why don&#39;t we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 424330.0,
      "end_time": 426330.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s wrong with us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 426330.0,
      "end_time": 427330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 427330.0,
      "end_time": 429330.0,
      "text": "Empiricism is inadequate"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429330.0,
      "end_time": 431330.0,
      "text": "because, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 431330.0,
      "end_time": 436330.0,
      "text": "scientific theories explain the seen in terms of the unseen."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 436330.0,
      "end_time": 438330.0,
      "text": "And the unseen, you have to admit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 438330.0,
      "end_time": 440330.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t come to us through the senses."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 440330.0,
      "end_time": 444330.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t see those nuclear reactions in stars."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 444330.0,
      "end_time": 447330.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t see the origin of species."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447330.0,
      "end_time": 451330.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t see the curvature of space-time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 451330.0,
      "end_time": 453330.0,
      "text": "and other universes."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 453330.0,
      "end_time": 456330.0,
      "text": "But we know about those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 456330.0,
      "end_time": 458330.0,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 458330.0,
      "end_time": 463330.0,
      "text": "Well, the classic empiricist answer is induction."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 463330.0,
      "end_time": 467330.0,
      "text": "The unseen resembles the seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 467330.0,
      "end_time": 469330.0,
      "text": "But it doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 469330.0,
      "end_time": 471330.0,
      "text": "You know what the clinching evidence was"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 471330.0,
      "end_time": 474330.0,
      "text": "that space-time is curved?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 474330.0,
      "end_time": 477330.0,
      "text": "It was a photograph, not of space-time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 477330.0,
      "end_time": 481330.0,
      "text": "but of an eclipse, with a dot there rather than there."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 481330.0,
      "end_time": 483330.0,
      "text": "And the evidence for evolution?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 483330.0,
      "end_time": 486330.0,
      "text": "Some rocks and some finches."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 486330.0,
      "end_time": 489330.0,
      "text": "And parallel universes? Again: dots there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 489330.0,
      "end_time": 491330.0,
      "text": "rather than there, on a screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 491330.0,
      "end_time": 494330.0,
      "text": "What we see, in all these cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 494330.0,
      "end_time": 498330.0,
      "text": "bears no resemblance to the reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 498330.0,
      "end_time": 500330.0,
      "text": "that we conclude is responsible --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 500330.0,
      "end_time": 504330.0,
      "text": "only a long chain of theoretical reasoning"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 504330.0,
      "end_time": 506330.0,
      "text": "and interpretation connects them."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 506330.0,
      "end_time": 509330.0,
      "text": "\"Ah!\" say creationists."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 509330.0,
      "end_time": 511330.0,
      "text": "\"So you admit it&#39;s all interpretation."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 511330.0,
      "end_time": 514329.0,
      "text": "No one has ever seen evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 514330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516330.00000000006,
      "text": "We see rocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 516330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519330.00000000006,
      "text": "You have your interpretation. We have ours."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 519330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521330.00000000006,
      "text": "Yours comes from guesswork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 521330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523330.00000000006,
      "text": "ours from the Bible.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 529330.0,
      "text": "But what creationist and empiricists both ignore"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 529330.0,
      "end_time": 531330.0,
      "text": "is that, in that sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 531330.0,
      "end_time": 534330.0,
      "text": "no one has ever seen a bible either,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 534330.0,
      "end_time": 538330.0,
      "text": "that the eye only detects light, which we don&#39;t perceive."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 538330.0,
      "end_time": 541330.0,
      "text": "Brains only detect nerve impulses."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 541330.0,
      "end_time": 544330.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t perceive even those as what they really are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 544330.0,
      "end_time": 546330.0,
      "text": "namely electrical crackles."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 546330.0,
      "end_time": 551330.0,
      "text": "So we perceive nothing as what it really is."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551330.0,
      "end_time": 554330.0,
      "text": "Our connection to reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 554330.0,
      "end_time": 556330.0,
      "text": "is never just perception."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 556330.0,
      "end_time": 560330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s always, as Karl Popper put it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 560330.0,
      "end_time": 563330.0,
      "text": "theory-laden."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 563330.0,
      "end_time": 566330.0,
      "text": "Scientific knowledge isn&#39;t derived from anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 566330.0,
      "end_time": 571330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like all knowledge. It&#39;s conjectural, guesswork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 571330.0,
      "end_time": 573330.0,
      "text": "tested by observation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 573330.0,
      "end_time": 577330.0,
      "text": "not derived from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 577330.0,
      "end_time": 580330.0,
      "text": "So, were testable conjectures"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 580330.0,
      "end_time": 584330.0,
      "text": "the great innovation that opened the intellectual prison gates?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584330.0,
      "end_time": 587330.0,
      "text": "No. Contrary to what&#39;s usually said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 587330.0,
      "end_time": 589330.0,
      "text": "testability is common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 589330.0,
      "end_time": 593330.0,
      "text": "in myths and all sorts of other irrational modes of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 593330.0,
      "end_time": 597330.0,
      "text": "Any crank claiming the sun will go out next Tuesday"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 597330.0,
      "end_time": 600330.0,
      "text": "has got a testable prediction."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 600330.0,
      "end_time": 603330.0,
      "text": "Consider the ancient Greek myth"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 603330.0,
      "end_time": 606330.0,
      "text": "explaining seasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 606330.0,
      "end_time": 608330.0,
      "text": "Hades, God of the Underworld,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 608330.0,
      "end_time": 611330.0,
      "text": "kidnaps Persephone, the Goddess of Spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 611330.0,
      "end_time": 614330.0,
      "text": "and negotiates a forced marriage contract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 614330.0,
      "end_time": 618330.0,
      "text": "requiring her to return regularly, and lets her go."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 618330.0,
      "end_time": 620330.0,
      "text": "And each year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 620330.0,
      "end_time": 623330.0,
      "text": "she is magically compelled to return."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 623330.0,
      "end_time": 625330.0,
      "text": "And her mother, Demeter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 625330.0,
      "end_time": 627330.0,
      "text": "Goddess of the Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 627330.0,
      "end_time": 632330.0,
      "text": "is sad, and makes it cold and barren."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 632330.0,
      "end_time": 635330.0,
      "text": "That myth is testable."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 635330.0,
      "end_time": 639330.0,
      "text": "If winter is caused by Demeter&#39;s sadness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 639330.0,
      "end_time": 643330.0,
      "text": "then it must happen everywhere on Earth simultaneously."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 643330.0,
      "end_time": 646330.0,
      "text": "So if the ancient Greeks had only known that Australia"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 646330.0,
      "end_time": 650330.0,
      "text": "is at its warmest when Demeter is at her saddest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 650330.0,
      "end_time": 653330.0,
      "text": "they&#39;d have known that their theory is false."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 653330.0,
      "end_time": 656330.0,
      "text": "So what was wrong with that myth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 656330.0,
      "end_time": 659330.0,
      "text": "and with all pre-scientific thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 659330.0,
      "end_time": 664330.0,
      "text": "and what, then, made that momentous difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 664330.0,
      "end_time": 668330.0,
      "text": "I think there is one thing you have to care about."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 668330.0,
      "end_time": 670330.0,
      "text": "And that implies"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 670330.0,
      "end_time": 673330.0,
      "text": "testability, the scientific method,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 673330.0,
      "end_time": 675330.0,
      "text": "the Enlightenment, and everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 675330.0,
      "end_time": 677330.0,
      "text": "And here is the crucial thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 677330.0,
      "end_time": 680330.0,
      "text": "There is such a thing as a defect in a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 680330.0,
      "end_time": 685330.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t just mean a logical defect. I mean a bad explanation."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 685330.0,
      "end_time": 688330.0,
      "text": "What does that mean? Well, explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 688330.0,
      "end_time": 691330.0,
      "text": "is an assertion about what&#39;s there, unseen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 691330.0,
      "end_time": 694330.0,
      "text": "that accounts for what&#39;s seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 694330.0,
      "end_time": 697330.0,
      "text": "Because the explanatory role"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 697330.0,
      "end_time": 699330.0,
      "text": "of Persephone&#39;s marriage contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 699330.0,
      "end_time": 701330.0,
      "text": "could be played equally well"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 701330.0,
      "end_time": 703330.0,
      "text": "by infinitely many other"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 703330.0,
      "end_time": 705330.0,
      "text": "ad hoc entities."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 705330.0,
      "end_time": 708330.0,
      "text": "Why a marriage contract and not any other reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 708330.0,
      "end_time": 712330.0,
      "text": "for regular annual action?"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 712330.0,
      "end_time": 715330.0,
      "text": "Here is one. Persephone wasn&#39;t released."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 715330.0,
      "end_time": 719330.0,
      "text": "She escaped, and returns every spring"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 719330.0,
      "end_time": 721330.0,
      "text": "to take revenge on Hades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 721330.0,
      "end_time": 723330.0,
      "text": "with her Spring powers."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 723330.0,
      "end_time": 728330.0,
      "text": "She cools his domain with Spring air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 728330.0,
      "end_time": 732330.0,
      "text": "venting heat up to the surface, creating summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 732330.0,
      "end_time": 736330.0,
      "text": "That accounts for the same phenomena as the original myth."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 736330.0,
      "end_time": 739330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s equally testable."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 739330.0,
      "end_time": 742330.0,
      "text": "Yet what it asserts about reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 742330.0,
      "end_time": 744330.0,
      "text": "is, in many ways, the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 744330.0,
      "end_time": 746330.0,
      "text": "And that is possible because"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 746330.0,
      "end_time": 749330.0,
      "text": "the details of the original myth"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 749330.0,
      "end_time": 751330.0,
      "text": "are unrelated to seasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 751330.0,
      "end_time": 755330.0,
      "text": "except via the myth itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 755330.0,
      "end_time": 758330.0,
      "text": "This easy variability"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 758330.0,
      "end_time": 762330.0,
      "text": "is the sign of a bad explanation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 762330.0,
      "end_time": 766330.0,
      "text": "because, without a functional reason to prefer"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 766330.0,
      "end_time": 771330.0,
      "text": "one of countless variants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 771330.0,
      "end_time": 773330.0,
      "text": "advocating one of them, in preference to the others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 773330.0,
      "end_time": 775330.0,
      "text": "is irrational."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 775330.0,
      "end_time": 777330.0,
      "text": "So, for the essence of what"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 777330.0,
      "end_time": 780330.0,
      "text": "makes the difference to enable progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 780330.0,
      "end_time": 782330.0,
      "text": "seek good explanations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 782330.0,
      "end_time": 785330.0,
      "text": "the ones that can&#39;t be easily varied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 785330.0,
      "end_time": 790330.0,
      "text": "while still explaining the phenomena."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 790330.0,
      "end_time": 793330.0,
      "text": "Now, our current explanation of seasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 793330.0,
      "end_time": 797330.0,
      "text": "is that the Earth&#39;s axis is tilted like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 797330.0,
      "end_time": 800330.0,
      "text": "so each hemisphere tilts toward the sun for half the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 800330.0,
      "end_time": 803330.0,
      "text": "and away for the other half."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 803330.0,
      "end_time": 805330.0,
      "text": "Better put that up."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 805330.0,
      "end_time": 806330.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 806330.0,
      "end_time": 811330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a good explanation: hard to vary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 811330.0,
      "end_time": 814330.0,
      "text": "because every detail plays a functional role."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 814330.0,
      "end_time": 817330.0,
      "text": "For instance, we know, independently of seasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 817330.0,
      "end_time": 819330.0,
      "text": "that surfaces tilted away"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 819330.0,
      "end_time": 822330.0,
      "text": "from radiant heat are heated less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 822330.0,
      "end_time": 825330.0,
      "text": "and that a spinning sphere, in space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 825330.0,
      "end_time": 828330.0,
      "text": "points in a constant direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 828330.0,
      "end_time": 831330.0,
      "text": "And the tilt also explains"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 831330.0,
      "end_time": 835330.0,
      "text": "the sun&#39;s angle of elevation at different times of year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 835330.0,
      "end_time": 837330.0,
      "text": "and predicts that the seasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 837330.0,
      "end_time": 840330.0,
      "text": "will be out of phase in the two hemispheres."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 840330.0,
      "end_time": 842330.0,
      "text": "If they&#39;d been observed in phase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 842330.0,
      "end_time": 844330.0,
      "text": "the theory would have been refuted."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 844330.0,
      "end_time": 849330.0,
      "text": "But now, the fact that it&#39;s also a good explanation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 849330.0,
      "end_time": 854330.0,
      "text": "hard to vary, makes the crucial difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 854330.0,
      "end_time": 856330.0,
      "text": "If the ancient Greeks had found out"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 856330.0,
      "end_time": 859330.0,
      "text": "about seasons in Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 859330.0,
      "end_time": 861330.0,
      "text": "they could have easily varied their myth"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 861330.0,
      "end_time": 863330.0,
      "text": "to predict that."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 863330.0,
      "end_time": 865330.0,
      "text": "For instance, when Demeter is upset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 865330.0,
      "end_time": 868330.0,
      "text": "she banishes heat from her vicinity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 868330.0,
      "end_time": 871330.0,
      "text": "into the other hemisphere, where it makes summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 871330.0,
      "end_time": 874330.0,
      "text": "So, being proved wrong by observation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 874330.0,
      "end_time": 876330.0,
      "text": "and changing their theory accordingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 876330.0,
      "end_time": 879330.0,
      "text": "still wouldn&#39;t have got the ancient Greeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 879330.0,
      "end_time": 882330.0,
      "text": "one jot closer to understanding seasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 882330.0,
      "end_time": 885330.0,
      "text": "because their explanation was bad: easy to vary."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 885330.0,
      "end_time": 888330.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s only when an explanation is good"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 888330.0,
      "end_time": 890330.0,
      "text": "that it even matters whether it&#39;s testable."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 890330.0,
      "end_time": 893330.0,
      "text": "If the axis-tilt theory had been refuted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 893330.0,
      "end_time": 895330.0,
      "text": "its defenders would have had nowhere to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 895330.0,
      "end_time": 898330.0,
      "text": "No easily implemented change"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 898330.0,
      "end_time": 900330.0,
      "text": "could make that tilt"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 900330.0,
      "end_time": 905330.0,
      "text": "cause the same seasons in both hemispheres."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 905330.0,
      "end_time": 908330.0,
      "text": "The search for hard-to-vary explanations"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 908330.0,
      "end_time": 911330.0,
      "text": "is the origin of all progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 911330.0,
      "end_time": 914330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the basic regulating principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 914330.0,
      "end_time": 916330.0,
      "text": "of the Enlightenment."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 916330.0,
      "end_time": 920330.0,
      "text": "So, in science, two false approaches blight progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 920330.0,
      "end_time": 923330.0,
      "text": "One is well known: untestable theories."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 923330.0,
      "end_time": 927330.0,
      "text": "But the more important one is explanationless theories."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 927330.0,
      "end_time": 931330.0,
      "text": "Whenever you&#39;re told that some existing statistical trend will continue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 931330.0,
      "end_time": 934330.0,
      "text": "but you aren&#39;t given a hard-to-vary account"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 934330.0,
      "end_time": 937330.0,
      "text": "of what causes that trend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 937330.0,
      "end_time": 939330.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re being told a wizard did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 939330.0,
      "end_time": 942330.0,
      "text": "When you are told that carrots have human rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 942330.0,
      "end_time": 944330.0,
      "text": "because they share half our genes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 944330.0,
      "end_time": 950330.0,
      "text": "but not how gene percentages confer rights -- wizard."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 950330.0,
      "end_time": 954330.0,
      "text": "When someone announces that the nature-nurture debate"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 954330.0,
      "end_time": 956330.0,
      "text": "has been settled because there is evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 956330.0,
      "end_time": 958330.0,
      "text": "that a given percentage of our"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 958330.0,
      "end_time": 962330.0,
      "text": "political opinions are genetically inherited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 962330.0,
      "end_time": 966330.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t explain how genes cause opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 966330.0,
      "end_time": 968330.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve settled nothing. They are saying that our"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 968330.0,
      "end_time": 970330.0,
      "text": "opinions are caused by wizards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 970330.0,
      "end_time": 973330.0,
      "text": "and presumably so are their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 973330.0,
      "end_time": 976330.0,
      "text": "That the truth consists of"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 976330.0,
      "end_time": 980330.0,
      "text": "hard to vary assertions about reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 980330.0,
      "end_time": 983330.0,
      "text": "is the most important fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 983330.0,
      "end_time": 985330.0,
      "text": "about the physical world."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 985330.0,
      "end_time": 988330.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a fact that is, itself, unseen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 988330.0,
      "end_time": 992330.0,
      "text": "yet impossible to vary. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 992330.0,
      "end_time": 996330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}